Elegant in her ebony coat, is stately Tootsie. Call her out to play, however, and she&rsquo;s all ears! &nbsp;Warm and affectionate, toot-toot Tootsie cherishes the time she spends with people, but especially with children (historically, Pit Bulls were called &quot;nanny dogs&quot;). Having never known how it feels to be truly and deeply loved, this most deserving of dogs deserves a second chance at a first, true loving home.

